nodes.docstring:
Decorator to wrap function in a scope_header.

Args:
    title: String or function returning string

Examples:
    @logtree.scope_header_decorator
    async def process_batch():
        ...

    @logtree.scope_header_decorator("Handling item")
    def handle_item():
        ...

